In the realm of [[application security]], the term '''Application Portfolio Attack Surface''' or APAS, refers to the collective risk to an [[organization]] posed by the sum total of the security vulnerabilities found within the set of all mission critical systems or [[software]] run by the organization or enterprise.<ref name="AppScan Tools and Tricks"/>

